    <item>
      <title>英国最低工资明年将上涨 6.7%，涨幅超过通胀率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-minimum-wage-to-rise-by-6-7-next-year-exceeding-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国最低工资明年将上涨 6.7%，以抵御通胀，这一增长将有助于财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 辩称，周三的预算保护了劳动人民，但可能会使英格兰银行的通胀对抗变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/uk-minimum-wage-to-rise-by-6-7-next-year-exceeding-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
